text: I Will, I Will... for Now is a 1976 American romantic comedy movie directed by Norman Panama and starring Elliott Gould, Diane Keaton, Paul Sorvino, Candy Clark, Victoria Principal, Robert Alda. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1976 comedy movies Category:1976 romance movies Category:1970s romantic comedy movies Category:1970s English-language movies Category:American romantic comedy movies Category:20th Century Fox movies
